.kg/1574727</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「習近平下台」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8cc51a3dfb1da70ae3b045dba6f38cc9045e7426","tid":1603520,"uid":84147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b444045a8afca565f3782cdd7fa57b1dd437bf","tid":1603520,"uid":161462,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T16:52:02.000Z","msg":"拎個打火機出嚟燒燒佢<br />\n仲可以有火屬性<br />\n<br />\n浸完屎水蝦醬 有屎屬性"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"1人1支"},{"pid":"6cdc8be1d2ea86f770a61f7a3c1aba0fcfab91db","tid":1603520,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:24:30.000Z","msg":"拉撚死你<br />\n真心唔建議 周圍都係人<br />\n燒烤叉咁撚尖 肯定瘋狂tk"},{"pid":"369667f30d9476e9774dabde2cdd4daaab903159","tid":1603520,"uid":326467,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:33:11.000Z","msg":"燒烤叉唔使俾錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n郊野公園燒烤爐隔壁回收筒大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb2cf106dee7c2c2ee5fb78fc45d4b9d8b4fa3c","tid":1603520,"uid":84147,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cdc8be1d2ea86f770a61f7a3c1aba0fcfab91db","tid":1603520,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:24:30.000Z","msg":"拉撚死你<br />\n真心唔建議 周圍都係人<br />\n燒烤叉咁撚尖 肯定瘋狂tk"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T17:40:57.000Z","msg":"點樣TK，咁耐以黎幾時TK左人<br />\n得把傘比狗打的就多"},{"pid":"086a36a55fd04d7bf25e04f71949982efa21b6dc","tid":1603520,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bb2cf106dee7c2c2ee5fb78fc45d4b9d8b4fa3c","tid":1603520,"uid":84147,"like":1,"dislike":0,